308
00:13:42,630 --> 00:13:43,610
Heading to Wushuang City?

309
00:13:44,120 --> 00:13:45,730
There's a ship docked at the east pier today.

310
00:13:46,550 --> 00:13:47,700
It will sail east and reach

311
