00:19:39,070 --> 00:19:42,060
The minimum bet is three liang of silver,

466
00:19:42,550 --> 00:19:45,220
and the maximum is an entire city.

467
00:19:46,750 --> 00:19:47,330
All right,

468
00:19:48,070 --> 00:19:49,260
