523
00:22:25,350 --> 00:22:26,460
Naturally.

524
00:22:26,720 --> 00:22:27,700
Our main city

525
00:22:27,720 --> 00:22:28,940
is Wushuang City.

526
00:22:29,030 --> 00:22:30,130
Its first City Lord

527
00:22:30,240 --> 00:22:31,540
helped Emperor Tianwu found his empire

528
00:22:31,750 --> 00:22:32,330
and was granted

